Package Scheduling

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeliveryList
    This is the object holding the list of activities and orders for the truck while the application is running.
    DirectionDistance
    The purpose of this class is to find the distance and direction of two entities based on the values for the two entities longitude and latitude which are then converted to miles to be able to tell the distance and then are analyzed with trig functions to find the direct needed to travel from the fist entity to the second
    LinearRegression
    Used to estimate output value from input variable through linear regression of the historical and related points.
    ScheduleChartObject
    This is used to return the values from the different scheduling options together to be viewed within the same chart with standard information base don the class of the object.
